name: Original Polaroid #3
description:
Instant Print made with Impossible Project experimental film.

from my series : MELT

to see the whole series visit my website.

After taking the photograph, I manipulate it using two different tools. Heat and, well, the other is my personal secret. Directly after the photograph is realized and starts to develop before my eyes, I manipulate patterns and mix colors. A long, but rewarding process.

Signed on the back in ink, with the date of the Month and Year when it was made.

To ensure the print last as long as it can, please keep out of direct sunlight, and out of very humid environments.
